Please note that past performance is not indicative of future results. The ratings listed above may not be representative of any one client's experience because these ratings may reflect an average or sample of the firm's accounts or composites of accounts. None of the publications listed above are affiliated with the firm, and the firm has not made any payment for or in anticipation of any rating. From time to time, the firm has, and the firm expects to continue, to purchase reprints and/or other publishing permission from certain of the publications that have recognized the firm's performance, including Informa Investment Solutions, Inc., the publisher of PSN awards. Since January 1, 2010, the firm has paid Informa Investment Solutions, Inc. the following amounts: $2,000 in 2012, $2,000 in 2013, $2,000 in 2014, $3,000 in 2015, and $2,000 in 2016 (through February 28, 2016). The above ratings are not based on client evaluations of the firm. We encourage you to contact the recognizing organizations if you would like additional information regarding their process or methodology. Please contact the firm should you have any further questions on our purchases of reprints or other publishing permission.
 






