Company Profile for Martin Investment Management, LLC | Business Wire
























































      Company Profile for Martin Investment Management, LLC
    





March 18, 2016 10:40 AM Eastern Daylight Time



--(BUSINESS WIRE)--Martin Investment Management, LLC is an equity oriented, majority 
      female-owned registered investment adviser located in Evanston, 
      Illinois. The firm focuses on three primary “Best Ideas” investment 
      strategies. The Growth with a Value Discipline strategy invests 
      primarily in U.S. large cap equities. The global Eco-Investing strategy 
      focuses on companies that have goals of engaging in best environmental 
      practices and good stewardship. The Tortue CapitalTM strategy invests in 
      a range of non-U.S. large cap companies in the developed world that have 
      global exposure through their products or services.
    




